\f0\b\fs28 \cf0 \strokec2 1. The Core Thesis\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa240\partightenfactor0

\f1\b0\fs24 \cf0 LocalPlus is a 
\f0\b Post-Search Discovery Layer
\f1\b0  for local economies. It replaces the "Keyword \uc0\u8594  Link \u8594  Click" model with an "Intent \u8594  Answer \u8594  Action" model. It is designed to be the "AdWords for the Generative Era," moving from competing for 
\f0\b Page Rank
\f1\b0  to competing for 
\f0\b Answer Inclusion
\f1\b0 .\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa280\partightenfactor0

\f0\b\fs28 \cf0 2. Technical Stack (Non-Negotiable)\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\sa240\partightenfactor0
\ls1\ilvl0
\fs24 \cf0 \kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 \outl0\strokewidth0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
\outl0\strokewidth0 \strokec2 Engine:
